Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足须小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个因为今天很热…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就穿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气热是要穿泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈 连濑奈也穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也穿泳裤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样又热又辛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我们蒙羞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很凉快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那身材…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太强壮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很粗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到老师这种出色的身材之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的胸口变得很难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我解开泳衣的带子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在又难受又辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱徒 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行还很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不快点起来工作的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被见张小姐骂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能再迟一分钟叫醒我的话
